Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.39,0:00:18.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know how much I will be able to\Ngive back in return for what I get from you.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.98,0:00:22.61,Default,,0,0,0,,But even so, I want to be with you from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.57,0:00:28.28,Default,,0,0,0,,That day, when Zen was leaving...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.86,0:00:32.62,Default,,0,0,0,,...he said, "See you later," as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.62,0:00:35.91,Default,,0,0,0,,That was reassuring.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.21,0:02:21.46,Def_Top,,0,0,0,,"Episode 12: Goodbye to the Beginning"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.83,0:02:54.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, it's so lively.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.00,0:02:56.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone looks like they're having fun.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.04,0:02:58.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Open Castle Day? What's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.67,0:03:00.54,Default,,0,0,0,,It's an event that happens once every few years
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.55,0:03:03.34,Default,,0,0,0,,where a corner of the castle\Nis opened up to the public.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.34,0:03:04.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.59,0:03:07.34,Default,,0,0,0,,There are various kinds\Nof entertainment, as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.34,0:03:10.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, us herbalists have work as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:10.97,0:03:14.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Once you reach a good stopping place\Nwith your work, you can go look.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:14.02,0:03:15.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.35,0:03:19.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Seems like something Zen would like.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.28,0:03:26.15,Default,,0,0,0,,That area is open right now,\Nso there are a lot of people, Shirayuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.15,0:03:26.90,Default,,0,0,0,,This way.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.90,0:03:28.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.99,0:03:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Shirayuki...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.54,0:03:34.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Prince Zen?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.25,0:03:38.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I think today will be busy,\Nbut I'm counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.17,0:03:39.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes, sir--
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.04,0:03:39.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave it to us!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.71,0:03:43.13,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, I was going to say that!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.05,0:03:48.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you know it was me right away?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.13,0:03:49.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I knew from your voice...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.93,0:03:52.22,Default,,0,0,0,,But why are you dressed as a guard?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.22,0:03:55.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I had some time, so I was\Nlooking around as I kept watch.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:55.93,0:03:59.56,Default,,0,0,0,,To see people in the castle at work,\Nand see how the citizens were doing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.56,0:04:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,There aren't many opportunities\Nto see both at the same time.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.86,0:04:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,That's very like you,\Nbut don't make anyone mad.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.90,0:04:08.95,Default,,0,0,0,,Also, Shirayuki, I thought\Nmaybe I'd be able to see you...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.95,0:04:10.32,Default,,0,0,0,,...just the two of us.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.32,0:04:11.74,Default,,0,0,0,,The two...?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.92,0:04:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Something dropped.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:21.12,0:04:23.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I-It's fine, it's fine!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.97,0:04:32.93,Default,,0,0,0,,You came too soon... you guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.10,0:04:35.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Did we interrupt, Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:35.60,0:04:37.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Shirayuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.14,0:04:38.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen, we were looking for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:38.77,0:04:40.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah. Even if the parts of the castle\Nthat have been opened up are limited,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.10,0:04:45.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought I told you to\Nnarrow your area of activity.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:45.44,0:04:47.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry for walking around on my own.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.78,0:04:49.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitsuhide was starting to panic.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.86,0:04:52.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Obi, you don't have to tell him that.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.07,0:04:54.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiki, do I still have time?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.62,0:04:55.95,Default,,0,0,0,,A little.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:55.95,0:04:58.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. What about you, Shirayuki?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.41,0:04:59.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.79,0:05:01.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, it's decided!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.46,0:05:05.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Why don't we go observe what's going\Non around the castle, the five of us?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.34,0:05:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Welcome! Welcome!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.30,0:05:17.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, there are food stalls, too?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.81,0:05:20.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We brought them in from\Nthe castle town just for today.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.11,0:05:28.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, there's alcohol, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.65,0:05:30.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't drink right now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.32,0:05:32.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.03,0:05:35.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Whoops. Look in front\Nof you when you run, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:36.03,0:05:37.83,Default,,0,0,0,,There are more people now.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:37.83,0:05:40.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Because it's almost lunchtime already.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:42.33,0:05:45.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? You wear stuff like that, Miss?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.71,0:05:47.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah, it depends on the place,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.84,0:05:50.80,Default,,0,0,0,,but when there are a lot of people,\Nit's easier to walk around like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.80,0:05:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh yeah? Now that you mention it,\Nyour hair does stand out.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:55.14,0:05:58.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Looks like something's\Nstarting on the other side.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.35,0:05:59.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what it is?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.85,0:06:01.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Shall we take a look?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.27,0:06:05.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Did Shirayuki run into some trouble before?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.69,0:06:11.07,Default,,0,0,0,,I see... Then, I can't blame her for hiding it.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.07,0:06:14.57,Default,,0,0,0,,I know. It's hard having idiots around.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:14.57,0:06:16.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Even though it's so pretty...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:27.25,0:06:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki--
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.13,0:06:29.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.17,0:06:31.63,Default,,0,0,0,,That day, I heard from Zen.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.34,0:06:36.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiki, Obi, Mitsuhide.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.84,0:06:42.22,Default,,0,0,0,,From now on, I will take a path that allows\Nme to be with Shirayuki in this kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:42.22,0:06:44.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I told her that that was what I wanted.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.73,0:06:46.44,Default,,0,0,0,,What did she...?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.06,0:06:50.07,Default,,0,0,0,,She took my hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.73,0:06:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Really, Zen?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.36,0:06:56.24,Default,,0,0,0,,I see...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:01.08,0:07:05.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen said that he would take a path\Nthat let him be with you from now on.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.58,0:07:07.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki, you want that, too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.50,0:07:11.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.21,0:07:15.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, do your best. We'll be with you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.30,0:07:16.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.60,0:07:25.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.02,0:07:29.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh? Where's Obi?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.06,0:07:30.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.24,0:07:40.49,Default,,0,0,0,,That's it! Nanaki wins!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.25,0:07:49.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Master! I won!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:49.96,0:07:51.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, here's the prize!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.59,0:07:53.55,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you doing going off on your own?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.55,0:07:55.21,Default,,0,0,0,,What the heck is Nanaki, anyway?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.21,0:07:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Times like that, it's cooler to use\Na fake name, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.51,0:08:00.30,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't understand it at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.30,0:08:05.85,Default,,0,0,0,,Forget about what's cool, I'm more\Ninterested in how you became so agile, Obi.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.85,0:08:08.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitsuhide, wanna fight me sometime?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.39,0:08:09.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, sure!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:09.81,0:08:12.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen, it's about time.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.15,0:08:14.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Well, see you later.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.48,0:08:15.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.86,0:08:19.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Obi, I'm leaving Shirayuki to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.20,0:08:25.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Let's go and see the\Nmaster when he appears, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.58,0:08:27.08,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.08,0:08:29.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Before that, Miss--
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.63,0:08:33.63,Default,,0,0,0,,You can have this.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:37.05,0:08:41.13,Default,,0,0,0,,It's the prize for winning.\NA hair ornament from another kingdom.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:41.14,0:08:43.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Make sure to show the master later.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.36,0:09:04.57,Default,,0,0,0,,--Prince Izana!\N--Prince Zen!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.91,0:09:08.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Prince Zen has become very dignified.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.37,0:09:13.25,Default,,0,0,0,,He looks like a different person.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.25,0:09:17.05,Default,,0,0,0,,--Prince!\N--Prince!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.05,0:09:20.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen, have you changed\Nyour thinking since then?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.22,0:09:21.97,Default,,0,0,0,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.97,0:09:25.10,Default,,0,0,0,,I was wondering what you\Nwere going to do with the girl.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.10,0:09:28.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Lord Brother, you wish to speak of that now?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.06,0:09:29.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.81,0:09:33.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course, I have been thinking about it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.20,0:09:36.94,Default,,0,0,0,,About the future...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.78,0:09:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.07,0:09:43.91,Default,,0,0,0,,I see him around the castle sometimes,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.91,0:09:46.70,Default,,0,0,0,,and there are times like what we just had...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.70,0:09:51.83,Default,,0,0,0,,The feeling that he's next to me\Nis still left in my ears and my hands...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:51.83,0:09:57.34,Default,,0,0,0,,But in this castle,\NI am still this far away from him...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.34,0:10:01.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Even so, Zen is always...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:05.76,0:10:07.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.14,0:10:08.85,Default,,0,0,0,,What will you do after this?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.93,0:10:11.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm, let's see...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:14.52,0:10:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Ryu!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.98,0:10:21.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you know where Shirayuki is?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.40,0:10:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Did something happen?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:22.78,0:10:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks like someone's been injured!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.28,0:10:29.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you trying to test me?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.58,0:10:32.12,Default,,0,0,0,,No, of course not--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.12,0:10:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, why did you say such a thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.00,0:10:38.29,Default,,0,0,0,,This is a place of celebration.\NIt is not fitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.29,0:10:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I just wanted to know\Nyou better, your highness--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.71,0:10:42.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.92,0:10:45.26,Default,,0,0,0,,She missed a step...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.30,0:10:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Pain medicine! Do you have pain medicine?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.72,0:10:50.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I still have to go on!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.51,0:10:51.22,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:51.22,0:10:52.06,Default,,0,0,0,,I said--
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.06,0:10:54.14,Default,,0,0,0,,O-Ouch...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.14,0:10:54.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Ow...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.94,0:10:56.52,Default,,0,0,0,,The bone is broken.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.52,0:10:59.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If you force it to move,\Nit'll take longer to heal, Miss.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.90,0:11:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,No...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.07,0:11:01.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:01.98,0:11:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,This play was supposed to do well\Nso I could be allowed into the castle
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.70,0:11:08.07,Default,,0,0,0,,and have the princes fall in love with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:08.07,0:11:10.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Is what she says.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:10.49,0:11:14.16,Default,,0,0,0,,You just want a reward so you\Ncan make new costumes, don't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.16,0:11:16.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! I'm an actress!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.79,0:11:18.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I want to stand on a\Ngrand stage in beautiful clothes,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:18.71,0:11:21.46,Default,,0,0,0,,and have my name known\Nthroughout Clarines one day...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:23.80,0:11:26.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh dear, how embarrassing.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.18,0:11:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No, I think it's cool.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.51,0:11:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Shirayuki.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.60,0:11:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Right.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.65,0:11:39.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Red hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.36,0:11:42.02,Default,,0,0,0,,First, I'll stabilize the injured part.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.02,0:11:44.36,Default,,0,0,0,,You... Will you stand in for her?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.36,0:11:45.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.24,0:11:46.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.36,0:11:49.57,Default,,0,0,0,,Please. Please go on stage as the princess!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.57,0:11:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:52.20,0:11:53.70,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.70,0:12:00.20,Default,,0,0,0,,I must see if that prince is\Nreally suitable for my princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.21,0:12:04.17,Default,,0,0,0,,However, the prince is careful,\Nand is never alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.17,0:12:05.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you ready?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.71,0:12:11.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I must hurry. It will be too late after\Nsomething has happened. Too late!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.34,0:12:14.18,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Here I go.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.18,0:12:16.43,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.52,0:12:19.97,Default,,0,0,0,,What's wrong, Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.97,0:12:22.68,Default,,0,0,0,,It... nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.69,0:12:26.36,Default,,0,0,0,,The one on stage right now is\Nthe knight who serves the princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.36,0:12:27.61,Default,,0,0,0,,The night before the wedding,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.61,0:12:31.07,Default,,0,0,0,,the knight will test the prince to see\Nif he is a suitable partner for the princess
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.07,0:12:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,by crossing swords with him.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.53,0:12:35.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Before that, there's just one\Nplace where the princess appears,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:35.53,0:12:37.57,Default,,0,0,0,,but she only has one line.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.58,0:12:40.04,Default,,0,0,0,,You can just follow my lead for where to stand.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.04,0:12:42.04,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I understand!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.04,0:12:44.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I can hide my hair, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.00,0:12:46.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes, it's better that way, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.63,0:12:48.71,Default,,0,0,0,,It's a waste, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.71,0:12:51.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I bet just that would make the audience happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.93,0:12:59.51,Default,,0,0,0,,I swear! Tonight, on my sword! On this body!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.51,0:13:01.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, you're almost up.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.73,0:13:05.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Show me what you've got!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.40,0:13:13.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You're the stand-in?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.65,0:13:15.49,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I look forward to working with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.49,0:13:16.41,Default,,0,0,0,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.41,0:13:18.03,Default,,0,0,0,,--Even if you tell me\Nto do that all of a sudden--\N--Shh!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.03,0:13:20.08,Default,,0,0,0,,It's fine, just do as I say!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.08,0:13:25.25,Default,,0,0,0,,If you do it, we'll definitely rise from being\Na third-rate troupe to being stars in no time!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.25,0:13:26.58,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm counting on you!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.58,0:13:28.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Fine...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.42,0:13:29.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay, do your best!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.75,0:13:31.59,Default,,0,0,0,,R-Right!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:37.55,0:13:40.85,Default,,0,0,0,,I hope the actress' injury wasn't too bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:40.85,0:13:42.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah... Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:43.48,0:13:44.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Something wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.77,0:13:47.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Kiki, is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.52,0:13:49.44,Default,,0,0,0,,...Shirayuki?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.03,0:13:58.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess! Please, listen to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.36,0:13:59.91,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yes!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.91,0:14:01.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Good, she got it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.45,0:14:04.24,Default,,0,0,0,,She's really nervous, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.25,0:14:05.45,Default,,0,0,0,,She'll be fine now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.46,0:14:10.50,Default,,0,0,0,,All she has left is to be\Nkissed on the back of her hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.50,0:14:12.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Is what she said. Master?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.59,0:14:13.50,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't allow it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.51,0:14:14.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.30,0:14:17.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course I can't. She's not an actor.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.26,0:14:19.22,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no need to go that far.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.22,0:14:21.14,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll go talk to the troupe leader.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.64,0:14:27.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder what's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.48,0:14:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,The prince is acting differently from usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:31.31,0:14:34.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess, will you pray upon my sword?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.36,0:14:40.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Princess...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.78,0:14:42.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, hurry!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.70,0:14:46.33,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you planning, Mr. Troupe Leader?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.54,0:14:49.33,Default,,0,0,0,,To expose the princess' hair?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.33,0:14:50.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.79,0:14:55.05,Default,,0,0,0,,After finding a stand-in with such\Nrare red hair, how could I leave it alone?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.05,0:14:56.38,Default,,0,0,0,,You know what...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.38,0:14:58.17,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't stop it now.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.17,0:15:01.13,Default,,0,0,0,,With this, our troupe\Nwill become a huge success!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.14,0:15:05.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Because her hair will lend the\Nbrightest color to our performance!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.97,0:15:10.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Here it comes! The climax of today's play!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.31,0:15:13.48,Default,,0,0,0,,You... are my wife.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.23,0:15:15.77,Default,,0,0,0,,You have to stop this quickly!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:15.78,0:15:18.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir Knight, a moment?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.86,0:15:20.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.91,0:15:22.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Wh-What are you trying to do?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.82,0:15:25.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't act stupid in front of my master.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.04,0:15:33.04,Default,,0,0,0,,That's not something for people to gawk at.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.05,0:15:43.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Stay back, Princess.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.22,0:15:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The sword to protect you is still mine!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.06,0:15:48.47,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.56,0:15:52.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Your highness, en garde!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.57,0:16:06.87,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry, herbalist!\NI almost couldn't keep my promise!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:06.87,0:16:08.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.24,0:16:09.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Good work.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:09.62,0:16:11.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Why is Zen...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.75,0:16:16.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, that? It's the job of the real\Nprince to protect the princess, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.25,0:16:19.71,Default,,0,0,0,,They must've been really important to him...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.71,0:16:22.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Your hair, and the kiss\Non the back of your hand...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.88,0:16:24.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh...?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:24.09,0:16:28.01,Default,,0,0,0,,The master looked like\Nhe really hated the thought of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:28.01,0:16:31.06,Default,,0,0,0,,He's so easy to read.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:31.06,0:16:33.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He's cool, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.61,0:16:39.11,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen always shows me...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:39.11,0:16:40.82,Default,,0,0,0,,...his feelings...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.82,0:16:42.61,Default,,0,0,0,,...and his passion...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.28,0:16:51.79,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I know, too, how important they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.14,0:17:10.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I didn't think I'd stand\Non a stage with you, Zen.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.01,0:17:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Seriously. I'd like to watch the same\Nplay as part of the audience next time.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:14.77,0:17:15.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.90,0:17:20.77,Default,,0,0,0,,But it was a strange experience being\Na knight drawing his sword against a prince.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.77,0:17:22.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I even got this mask.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.99,0:17:25.90,Default,,0,0,0,,It looks good on you, Sir Knight.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.32,0:17:28.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.57,0:17:31.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, I got it from Obi.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:31.54,0:17:34.33,Default,,0,0,0,,He said it was the prize\Nfrom the martial arts tournament.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.96,0:17:36.75,Default,,0,0,0,,That guy...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.75,0:17:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's kind of frustrating...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:38.92,0:17:40.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.38,0:17:42.46,Default,,0,0,0,,But it looks good on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.88,0:17:48.89,Default,,0,0,0,,I see. I guess I'll keep it on, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:48.89,0:17:52.60,Default,,0,0,0,,What did you do with your hair\Nwhen you were living in Tanbarun?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:52.60,0:17:54.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I walked around without anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:54.98,0:17:58.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Even after I moved to Clarines,\NI did the same, at first.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.15,0:18:00.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Now that you mention it, I guess that's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.86,0:18:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if it's okay to ask, but there's\Nsomething I've been thinking about for a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.74,0:18:07.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you run into problems?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.86,0:18:09.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Even before Raj.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.74,0:18:13.12,Default,,0,0,0,,There were a lot, but I didn't always lose.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.12,0:18:15.24,Default,,0,0,0,,My grandparents were very strong people.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.25,0:18:16.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Grandparents?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:16.37,0:18:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right. The two of\Nthem taught me a lot of things.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.54,0:18:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,They thought ahead to\Nwhen I would one day be alone,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.46,0:18:26.80,Default,,0,0,0,,and they said, even when there\Nisn't anything you can count on,
Dialogue: 0,0:18:26.80,0:18:32.55,Default,,0,0,0,,you can always keep trying your\Nbest at what you can do by yourself.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.56,0:18:34.81,Default,,0,0,0,,That's what they taught me.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.81,0:18:36.60,Default,,0,0,0,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:36.60,0:18:42.27,Default,,0,0,0,,I did think that you liked to do things\Nyourself instead of relying on others to help.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.27,0:18:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Their teaching was the basis of that, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.86,0:18:47.07,Default,,0,0,0,,But, recently...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.07,0:18:47.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.82,0:18:50.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I rely on you, Zen!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.66,0:18:56.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know if I'm showing you properly,\Nbut right now, I really am...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:56.66,0:18:59.12,Default,,0,0,0,,I think that's why I can do my best.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.12,0:19:00.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Really?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.71,0:19:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.79,0:19:04.71,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I didn't lose\Nsomewhere along the way...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.59,0:19:14.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen. Will you put out a hand?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.76,0:19:17.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Hm? Sure...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.32,0:19:34.66,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm glad I was able to come here, Zen.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.46,0:19:43.33,Default,,0,0,0,,I-I'm not used to stuff like this...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.33,0:19:44.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry if it was weird...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:44.79,0:19:47.96,Default,,0,0,0,,N-No, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.97,0:19:56.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, what're those?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.14,0:19:58.06,Default,,0,0,0,,It's your first time seeing them?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:58.06,0:20:00.98,Default,,0,0,0,,It's how Open Castle Day ends.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:00.98,0:20:03.56,Default,,0,0,0,,People wish on the lights\Nand send them into the sky.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:03.56,0:20:05.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Wanna take a closer look?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.36,0:20:06.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Yeah!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.36,0:20:07.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh, Shirayuki!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.32,0:20:14.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Just until we get outside.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.66,0:20:21.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:23.83,0:20:25.42,Default,,0,0,0,,Why are you calling my name?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.42,0:20:26.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't try to dodge the issue!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.67,0:20:30.01,Default,,0,0,0,,I told you to be careful of your actions!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.01,0:20:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Apparently, Mitsuhide saw the play.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.68,0:20:34.22,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.43,0:20:41.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Wow, it's so pretty!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.86,0:20:47.02,Default,,0,0,0,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.02,0:20:51.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Mitsuhide, you're always worrying\Nabout the master, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.44,0:20:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's because he's my beloved master.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.20,0:20:56.95,Default,,0,0,0,,When you fought and\Nhe wouldn't talk to you for a day,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.95,0:20:59.62,Default,,0,0,0,,you didn't eat a thing, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.62,0:21:01.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I endured it for a day!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.62,0:21:04.04,Default,,0,0,0,,When it went to two days,\Nthat was hard, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.04,0:21:07.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Two days? Woah, you're so childish, Master.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.88,0:21:09.59,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.59,0:21:12.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Listen, I talked to Shirayuki about this, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.80,0:21:17.43,Default,,0,0,0,,but I'm not planning to think\Nabout a future without you guys.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.81,0:21:24.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Zen, look! It's amazing!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.27,0:21:34.32,Default,,0,0,0,,He's kind of unfair sometimes, isn't he?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.32,0:21:36.36,Default,,0,0,0,,Because that's the kind of prince he is.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.36,0:21:39.70,Default,,0,0,0,,You're going to have a hard time, too, Obi.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.58,0:21:47.58,Default,,0,0,0,,On this path that we continue on,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:47.58,0:21:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,how many more chances will\Nwe get to have such peaceful times?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.30,0:22:02.43,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure I can find\Nhappiness in taking this path...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.32,0:22:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I will continue to walk\Non in order to find it...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.37,0:22:22.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Into the future with everyone...
